{"tid":1697671,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"平民唔關事？跑步都無得跑！大型賽事開始取消","createTime":"2019-11-07T03:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T06:20:05.000Z","uid":262445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1d44482a3171297b5cbc9d6bbd5417936283fc","tid":1697671,"uid":262445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"07-11-2019<br />\n2019年11月7日，香港 --- 聯合國兒童基金香港委員會（UNICEF HK）經審慎思量後，決定取消原定於11月24日假香港迪士尼樂園度假區及欣澳舉行的聯合國兒童基金會「為兒童跑」2019賽事。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於連串持續且不確定的因素，將可能影響賽事及各項安全措施的順利推行，為確保參加者、義工、受邀嘉賓及其他持分者得到最佳保障，尤其顧及到家庭及兒童參加者眾，經再三考慮後，UNICEF HK遂決定取消本年度賽事，這是令人遺憾且艱難的決定。<br />\n<br />\n我們衷心感謝所有響應「為兒童跑」的跑手及捐助者。為答謝支持，大會特別準備「感謝禮包」乙份，當中包括：<br />\n<br />\n-       完賽紀念獎牌<br />\n<br />\n-       號碼布<br />\n<br />\n-       adidas 港幣220元現金券，換領adidas運動服飾及用品<br />\n<br />\n-       運動冰涼毛巾<br />\n<br />\n-       感謝狀<br />\n<br />\n「感謝禮包」領取日將於12月初舉行，詳情將於本月底向確認跑手透過電郵公佈。另外，跑手將按已籌得指定善款金額，於當日領取「達標獎」禮品。<br />\n<br />\n若跑手希望退回捐款，亦可於2019年11月20日或之前填妥經電郵發送的網上表格以作安排。<br />\n<br />\n本會亦將於下屆開放「優先報名」名額，以答謝跑手們的支持，我們衷心希望於UNICEF「為兒童跑」2020再次見面！<br />\n<br />\n對於活動未能如期進行，本會深感遺憾，並對因活動取消而帶來任何不便，致以萬分歉意，祈請見諒。如對活動有任何查詢，請電郵至run@unicef.org.hk，或致電2833 6139（選擇語言後請按 [0] 字）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://run.unicef.org.hk/zh/NewsAndMedia/NewsDetails/106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frun.unicef.org.hk%2Fzh%2FNewsAndMedia%2FNewsDetails%2F106&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=def4511d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://run.unicef.org.hk/zh/NewsAndMedia/NewsDetails/106</a><br />\n香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"7f680d8bcc5a713d4ecc8b0a3e1a002bfa692eaa","tid":1697671,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvCTcoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvCTcoV.jpg&h=87c59ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樽頸突破！11 11 黎明行動 7:00 18區集合 行動強制罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"37ad3a5f3533769da82e3678060a95f09a3201b9","tid":1697671,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:05:08.000Z","msg":"黑警唔俾人跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed61a18834835eb38279f8f55083abec1abec319","tid":1697671,"uid":69891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"11。24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPoPo會睬你咩"},{"pid":"0cf186e55271caa770f54fb3fa232cb648e74bab","tid":1697671,"uid":2019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ed61a18834835eb38279f8f55083abec1abec319","tid":1697671,"uid":69891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"11。24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPoPo會睬你咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"本身都唔應該區選日搞活動"},{"pid":"e8103ba57e8b4b92e70827da84c9289033d49291","tid":1697671,"uid":261522,"like":0,"dislik